AND BEN &amp; JERRY’s ice cream!! I know! I’m excited too!

00:00:30.619 --> 00:00:38.460
What’s that you say? What IS nutrient recycling?
Well, let me tell you! It’s… it’s…

00:00:38.460 --> 00:00:45.940
trying to do something with all the poo…there’s
